{
  "_comment": "Transcript inventory for the Elite Recomposition Timer voice pack. Rendered with camilo-kokoro. Slug becomes the output filename (slug.wav). Structural cues use their existing runtime keys; coaching cues are numbered pool entries drawn randomly at runtime.",
  "items": [
    {
      "slug": "start_warmup",
      "text": "Welcome back, Camilo. Let's warm up. Set your intention. Let's build.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "structural", "phase": "warmup" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_complete",
      "text": "Warm up complete! Time to lock in. Let's work.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "structural", "phase": "transition" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "quarter_way",
      "text": "Quarter of the way there! Great pace. Keep that energy up!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "structural", "phase": "workout" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "halfway",
      "text": "Halfway! This is where the real work begins. Don't drop your standards now!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "structural", "phase": "workout" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "three_quarters",
      "text": "Three quarters done! Home stretch. Push through the burn. You've got this!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "structural", "phase": "workout" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "five_minutes",
      "text": "Five minutes left! Empty the tank!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "structural", "phase": "workout" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "one_minute",
      "text": "Final minute! Everything you've got. Leave nothing behind!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "structural", "phase": "workout" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_complete",
      "text": "Workout complete! Incredible work today, Camilo. Rest up. Come back stronger.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "structural", "phase": "completion" }
    },

    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_01",
      "text": "You showed up. That's the hardest part.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "intention" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_02",
      "text": "Set your intention. What are you here for?",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "intention" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_03",
      "text": "Leave the day behind. You're here now.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "intention" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_04",
      "text": "Ease in. There's no rush yet.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "intention" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_05",
      "text": "Build the focus before you build the effort.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "intention" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_06",
      "text": "Deepen the breath. Wake the body up.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "breath" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_07",
      "text": "Long inhale. Longer exhale.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "breath" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_08",
      "text": "Feel where the body is tight. Breathe there.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "breath" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_09",
      "text": "Let the blood move. Let the joints open.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "breath" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_10",
      "text": "Move with purpose. No wasted reps.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "form" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_11",
      "text": "Full range of motion. Don't shortcut it.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "form" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_12",
      "text": "Feel the ground. Plant every step.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "form" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_13",
      "text": "Warm the hips. Warm the shoulders. Warm the spine.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "form" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_14",
      "text": "Quality reps now pay off later.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "build" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "warmup_coach_15",
      "text": "The warm up is the workout. Treat it that way.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "warmup", "category": "build" }
    },

    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_01",
      "text": "Lock in! Right here, right now!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "presence" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_02",
      "text": "Eyes forward! This moment is yours.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "presence" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_03",
      "text": "Come back to your breath. Stay with it.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "presence" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_04",
      "text": "Nothing else matters. Just the next rep.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "presence" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_05",
      "text": "Right here! Right now! Nothing else.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "presence" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_06",
      "text": "Phone down! Head up! Stay present.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "presence" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_07",
      "text": "No coasting! Find another gear.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "effort" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_08",
      "text": "Don't let the tempo slip!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "effort" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_09",
      "text": "Harder than yesterday! That's the whole point.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "effort" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_10",
      "text": "If it feels easy, it isn't working!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "effort" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_11",
      "text": "The work is in the reps you don't want to do.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "effort" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_12",
      "text": "Push the pace! You've got more!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "effort" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_13",
      "text": "Shoulders down! Chest up! Core tight!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "form" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_14",
      "text": "Breathe through it. Don't hold your breath.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "form" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_15",
      "text": "Steady breath. Steady mind.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "form" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_16",
      "text": "Feet planted! Body aligned!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "form" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_17",
      "text": "Slow the eccentric. Control every rep.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "form" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_18",
      "text": "Squeeze at the top! Own the movement!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "form" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_19",
      "text": "Remember why you showed up today.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "purpose" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_20",
      "text": "This is the version of you you're building.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "purpose" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_21",
      "text": "Future you is watching! Don't let them down!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "purpose" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_22",
      "text": "You chose this! Now finish it!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "purpose" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_23",
      "text": "Discipline is showing up when it's hard.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "purpose" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_24",
      "text": "You're doing the work! Keep going!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "affirmation" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_25",
      "text": "This is what progress feels like!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "affirmation" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_26",
      "text": "One more rep! Then another!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "affirmation" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_27",
      "text": "Trust the process. Trust the reps.",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "affirmation" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_28",
      "text": "Stay with it, Camilo!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "affirmation" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_29",
      "text": "You've got this, Camilo!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "affirmation" }
    },
    {
      "slug": "workout_coach_30",
      "text": "Keep building, Camilo!",
      "metadata": { "cue_type": "coaching", "phase": "workout", "category": "affirmation" }
    }
  ]
}
